title: S13 Ep14: Doctor Strange and the Curses of Second Sight
itunes:title: Doctor Strange and the Curses of Second Sight
description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS is has a Ph.D in Strange Phenomena & asks you to turn your head and cough as we take a look inside the paranormal with Medical Intuitive Rachel Reimer.

Rachel Reimer is a medical intuitive. From a young age she has been able to feel & see things.
While recovering from a debilitating health challenge, she was forced to confront her gifts. Since recovering, she has been able to see, feel and hear things from spirit specifically related to health challenges.
Some funny...and some are altogether terrifying.
